lead_paragraph: MUELLER--John C. Holland Lodge No. 8 F&AM acknowledges with deep regret the death of our brother on January 21, 2016. Our sincere condolences are extended to his entire family. John R. Weber, Master James W. McGovern, Secretary 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  MUELLER, JOHN C
